Package: LLMMessageProcessor
Title: Process CSV Messages with LLM for Response or Embedding
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gavin", "Morgan", email = "hello@gavmor.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This tool ingests a CSV file containing messages, processes each row 
    using a Large Language Model (LLM) to generate responses or create embeddings. 
    It provides functionality for data ingestion, LLM interaction, and output handling.
